column2: GPS for 32' DEEP HOLE is N46-14.841 W90-1.680- sunny- light breeze- algae bloom today.
Bright sun- few clouds- light wind.
Clear and windy weather.  Ice out April 15th.
Clear with slight breeze.  Lake is 1 foot low with only slight rain in the last month.
Partly cloudy- hot- no rain of any amount in the last month.  Lake now 14" below normal.  Heavy boat and PWC traffic during 4th of July week.
Clear weather.  Lots of rain last month- lake now almost 20" above normal.  Lots of boat traffic this summer
Cloudy and cold (38 degrees). Weather cold and snowy last week and a half.  Some floating algae on lake.
weather sunny and breezy  lake is very low no rain lately  Ice out was april 15
Water level still low.  Very little rain.  Water is quite clear.
mostly sunny- warm- few clouds and north breeze
Finally have had rain and the lake is now above normal but there still is a lot of boat traffic including water skiers at this late date.
